EASTERN TO ATLANTA
MIAMI AND BEYOND.
All wide-body movie flights with connections to
over 50 cities in the U.S. and Caribbean.
ATLANTA
TALLAHASSE
ST. PELEAS
BRADENTON
FORT MYERS
PALM BEACH
* MIAMI
Sure, Eastern can take your
clients to Atlanta and Miami in all
wide-body comfort and they'll enjoy a movie on
board. But we don't stop there. Eastern has over 335 daily flights
ST MAARTEN
to/from Atlanta. And, over 250 flights to/from Miami. That means we can
connect your customers smoothly to over 50 other cities in the U.S. and Caribbean.
As you can see from the selected schedule on the reverse side, we've got some great
connections to speed passengers on their way. However, we haven't forgotten to take care
of them on the ground. In Atlanta, Eastern has two Ionosphere lounges for relaxing between
flights or a quick business meeting. Many times the connecting flight
is departing from the same concourse as the arrival gate. But if not, there are
underground trams and moving sidewalks between concourses. Or we've got a quickie, shortcut tunnel
right in the middle of each concourse for saving even more time and effort.
In Miami there is a plush Ionosphere Club between our concourses. And there is a brand new
international departures terminal for breezing in and out of the country.
Atlanta and Miami. Over 500 flights everyday on Eastern. Nobody can take better care of your customer's travel
needs to the East, Caribbean and even Latin America.
EASTERN
